item.title: Delete all resources
item.description: Start this section in a new Jupyter notebook with the Data Science kernel After running the workshop, you can remove the resources which you created using this helper function. First download the helper function. In a new cell execute the following. !wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/shashankprasanna/sagemaker-workshop-2021/main/notebooks/04_e2e_pipeline/utils.py%store -r Run the following command to delete all your project resources. You can also delete all the objects in the project’s S3 directory by passing the keyword argument delete_s3_objects=True.
